A woman has been charged with almost 100 offenses of underage sex with a 15-year-old boy.

Alysia Flynn, 32, is also suspected of being involved sexually with other students after police discovered she hosted drink and drug-fuelled parties at her Florida home.

Deputies in Viera, Florida, have launched a major investigation into Flynn after receiving information there could be other victims.

